data.description: Welcome home to this stunning 4 bedroom, 3 full bathroom property! With over 2,100 square feet of living space, this home offers plenty of room for your family to grow and thrive. The beautiful laminate flooring adds a touch of elegance, while the high ceilings create a sense of spaciousness. Sit back and relax by the cozy fireplace on those chilly evenings, or retreat to the master suite withits own walk-in closet. This remodeled home also features highly rated schools nearby, making it the perfect place to raise a family. The fenced yard offers privacy and security, while the new furnace and hot water heater provide peace of mind for years to come.  Located in a great commute location and boasting a picturesque view of the lake, this property truly has it all. Don't miss out on the opportunity to make this house your forever home - schedule a showing today!
